messages.message:
Hey , I have a PR removing a feature flag thats consistently failing CI with these tests erroring: `data-services/ray/model-training-worker (test): exit status 2`

This is the PR: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/59533/checks?check_run_id=27272572836

Does anyone know how to resolve this? I have seen other similar feature flag PRs pass CI in the meantime?
Hey! It seems like you had issues with updating python stub for the protos. Can you try running `cd webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked && make build-protos` again?
It ends up skipping that because it does not detect changes
but the CI seems to have a different problem.
You need to unstage the changes to the .proto file first.
